ps://post.smzdm.com/p/az5ege35/pic_25/' target='_blank'><img alt="腾讯极光S5 素人测评" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/02/5f2681862ee366725.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5ege35/pic_26/' target='_blank'><img alt="腾讯极光S5 素人测评" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202007/28/5f2004fb0ed2e7876.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5ege35/pic_27/' target='_blank'><img alt="腾讯极光S5 素人测评" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/02/5f268264df7289090.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">2. 4K片源测试（4K60帧）<br/></p><p itemprop="description">PX747与S5肉眼观感相差不大，近距离暂停拍摄时可见些许差异</p><p itemprop="description">PX747：（照片对焦有问题，非亲摄）﻿</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5ege35/pic_28/' target='_blank'><img alt="腾讯极光S5 素人测评" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/02/5f268369bae33731.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5ege35/pic_29/' target='_blank'><img alt="腾讯极光S5 素人测评" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/02/5f26836a09f5c8840.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5ege35/pic_30/' target='_blank'><img alt="腾讯极光S5 素人测评" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/02/5f26836a368ad1637.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5ege35/pic_31/' target='_blank'><img alt="腾讯极光S5 素人测评" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/02/5f26836a5e5576202.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">S5:﻿</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5ege35/pic_32/' target='_blank'><img alt="腾讯极光S5 素人测评" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/02/5f2683c07d7167070.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5ege35/pic_33/' target='_blank'><img alt="腾讯极光S5 素人测评" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/02/5f2683c0ac2412065.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5ege35/pic_34/' target='_blank'><img alt="腾讯极光S5 素人测评" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/02/5f2683c0e78ea4388.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5ege35/pic_35/' target='_blank'><img alt="腾讯极光S5 素人测评" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/02/5f2683c124fcf7318.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">用来对比的720P LG PH550G：﻿</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5ege35/pic_36/' target='_blank'><img alt="腾讯极光S5 素人测评" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/02/5f26846503ba83825.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5ege35/pic_37/' target='_blank'><img alt="腾讯极光S5 素人测评" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/02/5f268465304b13014.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5ege35/pic_38/' target='_blank'><img alt="腾讯极光S5 素人测评" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/02/5f26846565ab12462.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5ege35/pic_39/' target='_blank'><img alt="腾讯极光S5 素人测评" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/02/5f26846592af63863.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5ege35/pic_40/' target='_blank'><img alt="腾讯极光S5 素人测评" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/02/5f268465c34236314.jpg_e680.jpg" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">3. 动态补偿观感测试</p><p itemprop="description">自用的LG PH550G的刷新率为120HZ，玩游戏时无眼睛疲劳感。</p><p itemprop="description">用S5连接switch玩游戏时，动态补偿关时画面会感到细微不连续，眼睛容易疲劳（可能相当于30帧/秒。动态补偿强时画面流畅感增强，眼睛的易疲劳感下降（可能相当于60帧）</p><p itemprop="description">动态补偿关：视频不会传，参考上树文字<img alt="腾讯极光S5 素人测评" src="https://res.smzdm.com/images/emotions/27.png" class="face" /></p><p itemprop="description">动态补偿强：视频不会传，参考上树蚊子<img alt="腾讯极光S5 素人测评" src="https://res.smzdm.com/images/emotions/27.png" class="face" /></p><h2 id="cl_3">总结</h2><p itemprop="description">S5的清晰度介于全高清与4K之间（个人意见），比PX747略差。</p><p itemprop="description">自带<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/gaoqingbofangqi/" target="_blank">电视盒子</a>，资源丰富（大多4K资源及1080P需要VIP）</p><p itemprop="description">自动对焦功能很方便</p><p itemprop="description">3D功能未测试，不过本人感觉来说PH550G的120刷新率下3D观影时眼睛容易疲劳，S5的最大60帧（？）的条件下，应该是会更容易疲劳。（也可能不会，与画面清晰度也有关吧）</p><p itemprop="description">缺点也挺多，一时无法详述。</p><p itemprop="description">有兴趣留言，会抽空回答的。</p><p itemprop="description">总体来说，使用方便而且清晰度高，推荐购买的。（本人不知1080P的投影仪是如何表现，相对于低端4K的优派PX747来说）。</p><p itemprop="description">第一篇测评文章，请轻喷</p>
