rop="description">中间放入适量的红豆沙</p><p itemprop="description">第七步：左右网上拉开，卷起来</p><p itemprop="description">两角网外弯，成牛角状</p><p itemprop="description">第八步：放入烤盘，表面刷蛋液，撒芝麻</p><p itemprop="description">烤箱180°预热5分钟后放入烤箱中层</p><p itemprop="description">烘烤20分钟即可</p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a259vx0d/pic_27/' target='_blank'><img alt="入门级烘焙食谱，美味易做零失败！" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/02/5f2698d29cb997089.png_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">晚上空闲时做份牛角包</p><p itemprop="description">早餐牛角包配热咖啡</p><p itemprop="description">简直美滋滋~</p><p itemprop="description">小伙伴们原料买起来，动手做一做呀！</p>
