➜闲敲棋子落灯花 篇三：60224+30365航天飞机人造卫星与太空人
https://post.smzdm.com/p/a78z7n5g/	46837
<p itemprop="description">暑假给小朋友们买了几个航空航天相关的<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/LEGO/" target="_blank">乐高积木</a>，今天到的是60224和30365两个规模比较小的组合。</p><p itemprop="description">30365是一个卫星搭配一个宇航员的组合，塑料袋包装。60224是一架航天飞机搭配一个小卫星以及一个宇航员的组合。</p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a78z7n5g/pic_2/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/02/5f26a767d23f39931.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="包装正面"/></a>包装正面</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a78z7n5g/pic_3/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/02/5f26a76822f38272.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="包装背面"/></a>包装背面</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a78z7n5g/pic_4/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/02/5f26a7685c96f2325.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="包装正面"/></a>包装正面</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a78z7n5g/pic_5/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/02/5f26a768894c23327.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="包装背面（内有一纸说明书）"/></a>包装背面（内有一纸说明书）</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a78z7n5g/pic_6/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/02/5f26a768b8460303.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="60224全套（2袋零件+1贴纸+1说明书）"/></a>60224全套（2袋零件+1贴纸+1说明书）</span></p><p itemprop="description">小朋友花了不长时间拼完了，是这样的成品。﻿</p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a78z7n5g/pic_7/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/02/5f26a81040aa41984.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="全部组合"/></a>全部组合</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a78z7n5g/pic_8/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/02/5f26a8106dffa5649.jpg_e680.jpg" alt="30365带的卫星"/></a>30365带的卫星</span></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.